  "title": "BBS Scheduler",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle bored pile and Deep Soil Mixing overall drawing records.</li><li>Prepare bored pile and DSM shop drawing.</li><li>Review Client's construction drawing, and review subcontractor's shop drawing.</li><li>Keep track of shop drawing registry and submission  / approval status .</li></ul><p><strong>Role Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree or Diploma in Civil Engineering, Construction.</li><li>With 4 years of civil experience in Bored Piling / Deep Soil Mixing.</li><li>Proficient in MS Office and AutoCAD.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Ability to work collaboratively within a project team.</li><li>Location: Changi Airport</li></ul>",
